lass=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/8a80f8af7cf53de325a638e6df08149f.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the gold nuggets you will collect through your runs, you can purchase permanent upgrades at the blacksmith </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/af5700397389ecfbe8ee4ef91d9e3cbe.poster.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/af5700397389ecfbe8ee4ef91d9e3cbe.webm?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/af5700397389ecfbe8ee4ef91d9e3cbe.mp4?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/55cad006c93c3d46a178dc6ae129b9ad.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op and Steam Play Together are both available if you want to add a 2nd player to the run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/b9cc5e29d40e28ea60483a32caafc63f.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p>",
